msgid ""
":ref:`MX record <email-inbound-custom-domain-mx>` (requires advanced "
"technical knowledge)"
msgstr ""
":ref:`MX रिकॉर्ड <email-inbound-custom-domain-mx>` (एडवांस टेक्निकल नॉलेज की ज़रूरत "
